column9: How can a team display such good awareness one ball and then not even try the second run next ball? Raina was happy to sacrifice his wicket on the fifth ball of the over
Tye has missed an easy run-out. Hit straight to long-on
Nicely bowled by Tye but what an incredible shot from Kohli to bring up his fifty. He is down the wicket
Slower bouncer down the leg side
Recovers well again. Kohli jumps at Boland who seems to have done him in with a wider slower ball
Tye might have thought for a moment he has done Kohli in with a wide full ball as Kohli makes room
Another run-out between Kohli and Sharma. Low full toss hit towards deep midwicket. Sharma runs back for the second
Lovely placement again. Kohli jumps out of the crease
